@startuml 视频流每帧渲染流程
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFECE

participant "Camera/\n视频源" as Source
participant "VideoStream\n控件" as Video
participant "YUV→RGB\nShader" as Shader
participant "OpenGL\nRenderer" as GL
participant "EGL/Wayland" as EGL
participant "Weston" as Weston

== 视频流实时渲染流程 (60fps) ==

loop 每一帧
    Source -> Video: pushFrame()\nYUV 数据
    activate Video
    Video -> Video: 双缓冲切换\nping-pong buffer
    
    alt 使用 PBO 异步上传 (阶段四)
        Video -> GL: glBindBuffer()\n异步上传
        activate GL
        GL --> Video: 立即返回\n不阻塞
    else CPU 直接上传 (阶段一/二)
        Video -> GL: glTexImage2D()\n同步上传
        activate GL
    end
    
    GL -> Shader: 激活 Fragment Shader\nYUV 采样转换
    activate Shader
    Shader -> Shader: GPU 并行\nYUV→RGB 转换
    Shader --> GL: 转换完成
    deactivate Shader
    
    GL -> GL: 渲染到屏幕\n绘制全屏 quad
    GL -> EGL: eglSwapBuffers()
    activate EGL
    EGL -> EGL: 交换前后缓冲
    EGL -> Weston: wl_surface_commit()
    activate Weston
    Weston -> Weston: 与其他图层合成\n显示到屏幕
    deactivate Weston
    EGL --> GL: 完成
    deactivate EGL
    GL --> Video: 帧渲染完成
    deactivate GL
    deactivate Video
    
    note right: 目标：16ms 内完成一帧
end

@enduml
